===Transitive Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|baptiz|e}}
# To sprinkle or pour water over, or to immerse in water, as a [[spiritual]] cleansing process in the rite of [[Christian]] [[baptism]].
# To [[dedicate]] or [[christen]].
# {{vulgar}} Of rum, brandy, or any other spirits, to lower with water.
# {{vulgar}} To ensure proper burning of a [[joint]] by moistening the exterior with saliva.

